SQL_STMT_U.val: select c.ts_koop_verkoop_ind, a.tr_aantal, tr.trai_tr_account_code from :1 tv --TV_TRANSACTIONS_IN_PROGRESS inner join :2 tr --TV_TRIP_REL_ACCOUNT_INFO on tr.trai_tr_volgnummer = tv.trip_tr_volgnummer and tr.trai_tr_re_id = ~3 and tr.trai_tr_account_code in (1,3) inner join :4 a --TRANSAKTIES on a.tr_volgnummer = tv.trip_tr_volgnummer inner join :5 b --BELEGGINGSINSTRUMENT on b.be_volgnummer = tv.trip_tr_be_volgnummer inner join :7 c --TRANSACTIESOORTEN on c.ts_symbool = a.tr_indicatie where b.be_volgnummer = ~6 and (tr.TRAI_TRIP_TR_STATUS_BIT = 1 OR a.tr_transnummer = 0)
